com.facebook.buck.remoteexecution.util

Class OutputsCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.remoteexecution.util.OutputsCollector

  • public class OutputsCollector
extends Object
    A simple helper to collect remote execution outputs. Given a list of root output files/directories, it will construct all the Protocol.OutputFile and Protocol.OutputDirectory objects for the outputs offered by the delegate. It will also include a set of UploadDataSupplier for all the files and serialized data structures that are needed to expand the outputs on the client.
